title: Balance Training with Wobble Cushion!!!!
instructions: Follow video instructions
for safety, place a chair near you or stand next to the wall

title: Hip hike on step
instructions: Begin standing upright on a step
lower one leg off the step and let your foot hover above the floor
engaging your core move your hip up and down
stay strong on your standing leg without locking your knee

title: calf stretch on step
instructions: Begin by standing with both feet on a step
lower one heel, keeping your knee straight
hold here until time is up

title: soleos stretch
instructions: Begin by standing with both feet on a step
lower one heel, bending the knee of the lowered leg
hold here until time is up

title: seated shoulder flexion with cane over head
instructions: Sit upright in a chair, feet flat on the floor
grab hold of either end of a broom or cane and extend your arms above your head
bend your elbows and lower the cane behind your head
bring your arms back down and repeat

title: sit to stand
instructions: Sit on the chair with both feet on the floor
cross your arms against your chest (in an x shape)
stand up and sit down as many times as you can in 30 seconds

title: step up
instructions: Stand in front of a step
raise one leg onto the step
lift onto that leg, straightening your knee and lifting the opposite leg off the floor
bend your knee back down and bring the opposite leg to the floor, and repeat

title: step up with knee raise
instructions: Stand in front of a step
raise one leg onto the step
lift onto that leg, raising the opposite leg off the floor, until the knee reaches 90 degrees
lower the leg back down to the floor and repeat

title: Cool Chair
instructions: This is very cool chair trick
please sit down
please do the trick many times

title: wall squat
instructions: Stand upright, with your back against a wall and your legs hip-width apart and arms at your sides
bring your legs a few feet away from the wall
bend your knees and lower into a squatting position
hold for 2 seconds, then push your heels into the floor
return to standing position, and repeat

title: tandem walk
instructions: Begin standing upright with one foot in front of the other, heel to toe
walk forward, heel-to-toe in a straight line

title: Stretch-hamstrings supine with band
instructions: Lie on your back, with your legs outstretched and a band placed around one foot
raise your leg up while holding on to the band and keeping the opposite hip and leg on the floor
hold in this position

title: supine back twist
instructions: Lie on your back with your legs stretched out and your arms in a "t position"
bend one knee and drop it over the opposite side of your body, twisting your spine and lower back
hold this position

title: standing shoulder flex with stick
instructions: Stand with your legs hip width apart, feet flat on the floor
hold a broom or a cane in both hands, arms outstretched in front of you
raise your arms straight up over your head
lower and repeat

title: wall squat with ball
instructions: Stand with you back against a wall, legs hip-width apart and arms at your sides
place a ball between your knees and squeeze
bend your knees and lower to a squatting position, until your thighs are parallel to the floor or as much as possible
hold for 2 seconds, rise to standing position, and repeat

title: plank
instructions: Begin in a "push-up position" with your forearms on the floor
hold in this position until time is up

title: Standing heel raise
instructions: Begin standing upright, legs hip-width apart, while holding onto a stable surface
raise your heels off the floor
slowly lower them back to the floor and repeat

title: seated knee extension
instructions: Sit on a chair, feet flat on the floor
extend one leg forward, straightening your knee and lift your leg off the floor
hold for 2 seconds, slowly lower down and repeat

title: supine ankle pump
instructions: Lie on your back with your legs stretched out
flex your feet up and then point them down

title: supine ankle rotation
instructions: Lie on your back with your legs stretched out
draw circles with your feet
change direction

title: static quad
instructions: Lie on your back with your legs stretched out, toes pointed up
place a pillow beneath your affected knee
squeeze the muscles around your knee to straighten it
hold in this position

title: supine knee extension with pillow
instructions: Place a pillow beneath your affected thigh
lie flat on your back with your legs outstretched, your affected knee slightly bent on the pillow
straighten your affected leg, lifting the heel off the ground
hold for 2 seconds, lower and repeat

title: supine hip adduction with ball
instructions: Lie on your back with your knees bent, feet flat on the floor
place a ball or pillow between your knees
squeeze your knees together into the ball, then release and repeat

title: Calf stretch
instructions: Stand near a wall with one foot in front of the other, front knee slightly bent
keep your back knee straight, your heel on the ground, and lean toward the wall
feel the stretch all along the calf of your back leg
hold this stretch for 20-30 seconds and alternate stretching the other leg

title: walk sideways
instructions: Begin standing upright
take a step to the side then bring your standing foot to meet the other leg
continue until time is up

title: 3rd warrior
instructions: Xx frfrd

title: tree pose
instructions: Stand upright
shift your weight toward one foot and slide the other foot above the standing knee
hold until time is up

title: groin stretch
instructions: Begin by kneeling on the floor, with your back straight and hands on your hips
shift your hips forward until you feel a stretch along the front of your back thigh
hold until time is up

title: cobra
instructions: Lie on your stomach with your legs outstretched
place both palms flat on the floor beside you
curl your chest up and away from the floor
hold in this position

title: finger extension
instructions: Rest your hand on a stable surface, with your palm face down and fingers spread out
lift one finger straight up, hold for 2 seconds, then lower back down and progress to the next finger until completing the entire hand
repeat

title: finger opposition
instructions: Resting your elbow on a stable surface, touch your thumb to each of your four fingers, one at a time, making an "o" shape
after each finger, straighten your fingers and repeat

title: wrist extension
instructions: Begin by resting your arm on a stable surface, with your wrist and palm leaning over the edge
raise your wrist, extending all five fingers straight up
hold for 2 seconds, lower back down and repeat

title: prone knee flexion with band
instructions: Lie flat on your stomach with a band placed around your ankle
reach behind you with both hands to take hold of the band
bend your knee, reaching your heel toward your buttocks and hold

title: steated butterfly
instructions: Sit on the floor with your legs in butterfly position (knees bent, feet pressing against one another)
hold your ankles with your hands and rest your elbows on your knees
hold until time is up

title: supine leg press with band
instructions: Lie flat on your back with one leg outstretched and the other bent toward you
wrap a band around the foot of your bent leg
while holding the band with both hands, straighten the bent leg, then bring the knee back toward you, and repeat

title: neck side flexion
instructions: Sit on a chair, feet flat on the floor
bend your neck sideways to bring your ear toward your shoulder
hold for 5 seconds, then slowly return to neutral and repeat on the opposite side

title: sit to stand - affected side
instructions: Sit on a chair with both feet flat on the floor
slide your affected leg toward you, keeping your foot on the floor
your other foot should be forward out also on the floor
raise your arms straight out in front of you, holding them parallel to the floor
lean forward and raise up to a standing position
sit back down, and repeat

title: half forward fold
instructions: Begin standing upright, several feet behind the back of a chair
raise your arms overhead and hinge forward from the hips
grasp the back of the chair, hold here and breathe

title: quad stretch
instructions: Stand facing a stable surface
bend the knee back as far as possible toward your buttocks by holding your ankle, with one hand
hold here

title: side flexion
instructions: Stand with your legs hip width apart, feet flat on the floor
engage your core, then slide one hand down your side
hold for 10 seconds, then push back up and repeat

title: shoulder external rotation with band
instructions: Tie one end of a band to a doorknob
stand parallel to the door, and a few feet away
hold the loose end of the band with one hand, keeping your elbow tucked beside your body
rotate your arm to the side, keeping your elbow in place
return to starting position, and repeat

title: seated chest press with band
instructions: Sit upright on a chair, feet flat on the floor
place a band underneath your buttocks and grab hold of either end with both hands
extend one arm forward
hold for 2 seconds, then bend your elbow back to starting position and repeat on the opposite side
alternate between both sides

title: seated biceps with band
instructions: Sit upright on a chair, feet flat on the floor
place a band underneath your buttocks and grab hold of either end
bend both elbows toward your chest
hold for 2 seconds, lower back down and repeat

title: step tap alternating leg
instructions: Stand facing a stepת keep your feet hip-width apart
begin tapping your toes on the step in front of you, alternating feet

title: Clamshell exercise left
instructions: Lie on your side, with legs stacked and knees bent at a 45-degree angle
rest your head on your lower arm, and use your top arm to steady your frame
engage your abdominals by pulling your belly button in, as this will help to stabilize your spine and pelvis
keeping your feet touching, raise your upper knee as high as you can without shifting your hips or pelvis
don’t move your lower leg off the floor
pause, and then return your upper leg to the starting position on the ground

title: toe walk
instructions: Begin standing upright, legs hip-width apart
lift your heels off the ground and put your weight on your toes
while standing on your toes, walk in a straight line

title: heel walk
instructions: Begin standing upright, legs hip-width apart
lift your toes off the ground and put your weight on your heels
while standing on your heels, walk in a straight line

title: half tree pose
instructions: Stand upright
shift your weight toward one foot and slide the other foot below the standing knee
hold until time is up

title: TFL stretch
instructions: Stand beside a wall, with one hand resting on the wall for support
cross the leg closest to the wall behind the other and lean your hips toward the wall, while extending the hand furthest from the wall down beside your hip
relax your shoulders and neck, and hold

title: seated ankle stretch PF
instructions: Sit on a chair with your feet flat on the floor
cross one ankle over the opposite knee
grab hold of your foot and point your toes
make sure the movement comes from both the ankle and the toes
use your hand to enhance the stretch, and hold

title: hip lift on chair
instructions: Lie flat on your back, both heels resting on a sturdy chair
with arms at your sides, press into your heels to lift your hips
hold for 5 seconds, return to starting position and repeat

title: lateral lunge
instructions: Stand upright, feet hip-width apart
take one big step to the side, while keeping your torso upright, until the knee of your leading leg is bent at around 90°
keep your trailing leg straight
alternate between both sides

title: seated back twist
instructions: Sit on a chair with your feet flat on the floor
straighten your back and turn towards the back of the chair
one hand resting on the seat behind you, the other on your thigh
hold this position

title: squat
instructions: Begin standing upright with your legs hip-width apart
press your hips back, bend your knees, and lower yourself as far as you can without leaning your upper body more than a few inches forward
push your heels into the floor and straighten your legs, returning to standing, and repeat

title: supine shoulder flexion with stick
instructions: Lie flat on your back with your legs stretched out
grab hold of either end of a broom or cane extend your arms above and behind your head
bring your arms back down
repeat

title: backward Walking
instructions: Begin standing upright, legs hip width apart
make sure there are no obstacles behind you
facing forward, slowly walk backwards, keeping your back upright and your eyes looking forward

title: tandem stand
instructions: Stand upright with one foot in front of the other, heel to toe
hold in this position

title: cat cow
instructions: Begin on your hands and knees in a "table-top" position
inhale as you drop your belly towards the mat
lift your chin and chest, and gaze up toward the ceiling
as you exhale, draw your belly to your spine and round your back toward the ceiling
release the crown of your head toward the floor, but don't force your chin to your chest
come back into cow pose

title: grip exercise with ball
instructions: Resting your elbow on a stable surface, place a ball in the palm of your hand
squeeze the ball, hold for 2 seconds, then release and repeat

title: clothes pin pinch
instructions: Resting your elbow on a stable surface, place a clothes pin between your thumb and index finger
pinch and release with all fingers

title: seated ankle stretch with strap
instructions: Sit on a chair or on the floor, one foot flat on the floor, the other leg extended, foot resting on a chair in front of you
wrap a band around this foot, keeping your toes flexed
bring your toes toward you and hold in this position

title: seated butterfly with pillows
instructions: Sit upright with your legs in butterfly position (knees bent, feet pressing against one another)
hold your ankles with your hands and rest your elbows on your knees
hold in this position until time is up

title: high plank
instructions: Begin in a "push-up position" with your hands on the floor
hold in this position until time is up

title: seated shoulder flexion with cane
instructions: Sit upright in a chair, feet flat on the floor
grab hold of either end of a broom or cane and extend your arms above your head
bring your arms back down and repeat

title: child pose
instructions: Kneel on the floor with your ankles together and your knees hip-width apart
rest your palms on top of your thighs
lower your torso between your knees
extend your arms in front of you, palms facedown, or, relax your arms alongside your body

title: supine hip rotator
instructions: Lie on your back with your knees bent
place one ankle on the thigh of the opposite leg
push the knee slowly away
hold this position until time is up

title: roll up
instructions: Lie on your back with your legs outstretched and your arms resting straight beside your ears
lift your arms forward, then lift your head, neck and shoulders off the floor, peeling your back up to a seated position
curl your back and slowly lower back down to the starting position, and repeat

title: Core training - dead bug
instructions: Lie on your back with your knees bent, feet flat on the floor
raise your right hand straight behind your head and your left leg straight forward, pulling in opposite directions
alternate between both sides

title: triceps stretch
instructions: Stand upright with your legs hip-width apart, knees slightly bent
bend the arm you would like to stretch behind you, so that your palm is between your shoulder blades
grab hold of your elbow with your other hand and hold

title: deltoid stretch
instructions: Stand upright with your legs hip-width apart, knees slightly bent
reach one arm across your chest
wrap your other arm around your reaching arm and pull it toward you to increase your stretch
hold here until time is up

title: standing hamstrings stretch
instructions: Begin standing next to a step, with your legs hip width apart
lift/ raise the leg you would like to stretch onto the step, and hinge forward at your hips
keep your knee extended and hold in this position

title: butterfly on wall
instructions: Lie flat on your back with both legs raised into a butterfly position (knees bent, feet pressing against one another) against the wall
hold in this position until time is up

title: prone hip internal rotation
instructions: Lie flat on your stomach with your knees bent and feet together, heels facing the ceiling
lower both feet in opposite directions, lowering toward the floor
return to the starting position and repeat

title: Seated heel Raises
instructions: Start seated with your feet flat on the floor
rest your hands on your lap or the sides of your chair
lift your heel, keeping the other foot planted firmly on the ground
hold for 3 seconds lower back down
switch to the other leg
repeat until time is up

title: palm to palm and back to back
instructions: Sit on a chair, feet flat on the floor or stand up
bring your hands together in front of you, palm to palm, at heart level
lower your hands down toward your belly button, keeping the heels of your hands together
flip your hands so that their touching back to back and slide them back up to your heart
repeat

title: wall push ups
instructions: Begin standing upright, facing the wall
place both hands on the wall, arms length away and shoulder-width apart
bend your elbows to lean toward the wall, push back until arms are straight
repeat

title: seated weight bearing elbow
instructions: Sit upright in a chair or bed, feet flat on the floor
leaning to your affected side, press your elbow onto the bed or a chair beside you, and lean onto that arm
hold in this position until time is up

title: seated weight bearing arm
instructions: Sit upright on a chair or bed, feet flat on the floor
press your affected hand onto the bed or chair beside you, and lean onto that arm, keeping it straight
hold in this position until time is up

title: shoulder pendulum
instructions: Begin standing beside a stable surface
lean over the surface, with your unaffected arm resting on the surface and supporting your weight
relax the affected arm and let it hang loosely
slowly swing your hand in a circle, gradually making the circle bigger if you can

title: superman
instructions: Lie on your stomach with your arms and legs extended outward
lift your head, one arm and the opposite leg off the floor
extend them in opposite directions
hold in this position until time is up

title: standing shoulder ext with cane
instructions: Stand upright, legs hip width apart
grab hold of either end of a broom or cane, your arms extended behind your back
raise your arms up and away from the floor, expanding your chest
bring your arms back down and repeat

title: squat with band
instructions: Stand upright, legs hip width apart and feet flat on the floor
wrap a band around your legs at mid thigh press your hips back, bend your knees, and lower your body slightly, hinging at your hips
push your heels into the floor and straighten your legs, repeat

title: butterfly crunch
instructions: Lie on your back with your legs in butterfly position, knees bent
soles of your feet pressing against one another
place your hands behind your head and engage your core
slowly raise your upper body slightly off the floor
slowly lower and repeat

title: abdominal crunch
instructions: Lie on your back with your hands resting behind your head
press your lower back against the floor and engage your core
while keeping your neck in a neutral position, slowly lift your upper body off the floor until just your upper back is raised
lower back down and repeat

title: knee flexion ROM on step
instructions: Stand in front of a step
place one foot on the step and keep your other leg straight on the floor
move your body forward, bending the knee on the step as you move, then hold

title: knees to chest
instructions: Lie on your back with your knees bent, feet flat on the floor
bring your knees to your chest one by one
grab onto your knees, and hold

title: shoulder flexion on wall
instructions: Begin standing upright, facing a wall
slide one hand up the wall above your head, and hold

title: shoulder abduction on wall
instructions: Begin standing upright with a wall to your side
slide the hand up the wall, then lower and repeat

title: supine heel slide
instructions: Lie on your back with your legs stretched out, toes pointed up, heels on the floor
slide one heel toward your buttocks then slide it forward again and repeat

title: clamshell
instructions: Lie on your side, legs stacked and knees bent at a 45-degree angle
rest your head on your lower arm
use your other arm to maintain balance
keeping your feet touching, raise your top knee as high as you can without shifting your hips or pelvis
hold for 2 seconds, then bring your knee back down and repeat

title: supine knee extension with band
instructions: Lie flat on your back with your legs outstretched
wrap a band around one foot and hold it with both hands
raise your leg straight up and hold

title: superwoman
instructions: Lie on your stomach with your arms and legs extended outward
lift your head, one arm and the opposite leg slightly off the floor
extend them in opposite directions
hold for 2 seconds, then lower
alternate between both sides

title: sit to stand squat
instructions: Sit on a chair with both feet on the floor
raise your arms straight out in front of you and parallel to the floor
lean forward and raise up to standing position
lower back down toward the chair, and rise up again without sitting down
repeat

title: step tap same leg
instructions: Stand facing a step
lean toward one leg and begin tapping the toes of the opposite leg on the step

title: step down
instructions: Stand on a step
step down with one foot
push back up and place that foot back on the step, and repeat

title: step up sideways
instructions: Stand with both feet on a step
bring one leg down to your side to touch the floor
push back up and place that foot back up on the step, and repeat

title: single leg stance
instructions: Stand upright
shift your weight toward one foot and lift the other foot off the floor
hold until time is up

title: single leg stance- eyes closed
instructions: Stand upright
shift your weight toward one foot and lift the other foot off the floor
close your eyes
hold until time is up

title: standing knee flexion
instructions: Begin standing upright with your hands resting on a stable surface
lift one foot off the floor and bend your knee backwards
lower and repeat

title: standing hip abduction
instructions: Begin standing upright with your hands resting on a stable surface
raise one leg out beside you
hold for 2 seconds, lower and repeat

title: standing hip extension
instructions: Begin standing upright with your hands resting on a stable surface
lift your leg behind you, hold for 2 seconds, lower and repeat

title: standing hip flexion
instructions: Begin standing upright with your hand resting on a stable surface on your side
raise one knee up (imagine you're balancing a penny on your knee)
hold for 2 seconds, lower and repeat

title: walk sideways with band around ankles
instructions: Begin standing upright with a band wrapped around your ankles
take a step to the side then bring your standing foot to meet the other leg
continue until time is up

title: shoulder flex with stick behind head
instructions: Stand upright with your legs hip-width apart, knees slightly bent
grab hold of either end of a broom or cane and extend your arms above your head
bending your elbows, lower the stick/ cane behind your head
bring your arms back down and repeat

title: prone knee flexion
instructions: Lie flat on your stomach with both legs outstretched
bend one knee, reaching your heel toward your buttocks and hold
rest in this position

title: clamshell with band
instructions: Wrap a band around your legs at mid-thigh level
rotate to lie on your side, legs stacked and knees bent at a 45-degree angle
rest your head on your lower arm
keeping your feet touching, raise your top knee as high as you can without rotating your hips or pelvis
hold for 2 seconds, and then slowly bring your knee back down and repeat

title: supine shoulder external rotation
instructions: Lie on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the floor
holding a broom or cane between both hands, lower the cane to one side, while keeping your elbows bent and close to your chest
then return to center and alternate between both sides

title: prone hip extension
instructions: Lie on stomach with a pillow under your hips
extend your leg straight back, and raise it slightly off the floor
lower and repeat

title: side plank
instructions: Lie on your side, legs stacked and straight, propped up on your forearm
lift your hips off the floor
hold until time is up

title: single leg hip raise
instructions: Lie on your back with one leg bent and the other leg extended on the floor
keeping your extended leg straight, lift it up to a 45-degree angle so that it is in line with the opposite thigh
with your arms by your side, press your standing heel into the floor and lift your hips to form a straight line from hip to foot
hold in this position for 2 seconds, then lower down and repeat

title: supine hip abduction slides
instructions: Lie on your back with your legs outstretched, toes pointing up
slide one leg straight out to the side, return to center and repeat

title: knee to chest (single knee)
instructions: Lie on your back with your legs outstretched
bring one knee toward your chest and grab ahold of it, keeping the opposite leg straight on the floor
hold this position until time is up

title: supine bent knees march
instructions: Lie on your back with your knees bent, feet flat on the floor
lift one foot off the floor, bending the knee toward your chest, then lower down
alternate between both sides, marching in place

title: side plank knees bent
instructions: Lie on your side, legs stacked and knees bent, propped up on your forearm
lift your hips off the floor
hold until time is up

title: seated foot inversion
instructions: Sit on a chair and cross your ankle over the opposite knee, your other foot flat on the floor
wrap a band around the ball of the raised foot and hold on to the band with both hands, anchoring it onto your raised knee
lift your big toe toward the ceiling, hold for 2 seconds, lower back down and repeat

title: seated hip abduction with band
instructions: Sit upright in a chair, feet flat on the floor
place a band around the middle of your thighs
push your knees in opposite directions while keeping both feet flat on the floor
hold for 2 seconds, return to center and repeat

title: seated hip adduction with ball
instructions: Sit upright in a chair, feet flat on the floor
place a ball between your knees
push your knees together, while keeping both feet flat on the floor
hold for 2 seconds, release and repeat

title: seated core and arm strength
instructions: Sit upright in a chair, feet flat on the floor
raise your arms in front of you to shoulder level and cross your fingers together
hinge your hips forward, leaning your back straight forward
hold for 2 seconds, lean back, return to starting position and repeat

title: seated external rotation of arms
instructions: Sit on a chair, feet flat on the floor
hold both ends of a band, one in each hand
tuck your elbows by your side, with your hands extended at a 90 degree angle
pull the band in oppisite directions, creating resistance in the band
hold for 2 seconds, release and repeat

title: seated hip flexion/ tap exercise
instructions: Sit on a chair with your feet flat on the floor
lift one foot off the floor, raising your hip up
lower and repeat on the other side, alternating between both legs

title: hip rotator stretch
instructions: Sit on a chair and cross your ankle over the opposite knee, your other foot flat on the floor
use your hand to lightly push down the raised knee
lean forward toward your knees while keeping a straight back
hold

title: seated APT/PPT
instructions: Sit on a chair with your feet flat on the floor, shoulders relaxed
engage your core, inhale and roll your hips forward
arch your back and bring your shoulderblades together
as you exhale- roll your hips back, roll your back and move your shoulder blades away from one another
repeat

title: seated Hamstring stretch
instructions: Sit on a chair with your feet flat on the floor
extend the leg you would like to stretch forward, toes raised and heel on the floor
hinge at the hips and lean forward toward your outstretched leg, while keeping your back straight
hold
you should feel a stretch at the back of your knee

title: fist to open hand
instructions: Sit or stand, and fold inward the wrist of your affected hand using your unaffected side
slowly open the fingers and apply light pressure to help extend and open the hand
hold until time is up

title: seated neck rotation
instructions: Sit on a chair, feet flat on the floor
slowly turn your neck to one side while keeping your shoulders relaxed
hold for 5 seconds, return to neutral position and then repeat on the opposite side

title: triple extension of leg
instructions: Stand facing arms length away from a wall, with your legs hip width apart
lean on the wall with your hands for support
lift one leg toward your chest while lifting onto the heel of your standing foot
hold for 2 seconds, then lower back down and repeat

title: side walk with band around foot
instructions: Begin standing upright with a band wrapped around the ball of your feet
take a step to the side then bring your standing foot to meet the other leg, do 10 steps in each direction

title: side walk with long band
instructions: Begin standing upright, then step onto the middle of a band, holding the ends of the band at hip height
take a step to the side then bring your standing foot to meet the other leg
take 10 steps in each direction

title: hip hinge
instructions: Stand upright with your legs hip width apart, knees slightly bent
grasping either end of a broom or cane, hinge at the hips and bend forward
then engage your core and buttocks and return to standing
repeat

title: deadlift
instructions: Stand upright with your legs hip width apart, knees slightly bent
grasping either end of a broom or cane, hinge at the hips and bend forward
lower your arms toward the floor and keep your back straight

title: modified groin stretch
instructions: Stand beside a chair and raise the knee of the leg you would like to stretch onto the chair
your other leg should remain standing on the floor
slowly shift your hips forward until you feel a stretch along the front of your lifted thigh
hold until time is up

title: standing heel rise- single leg
instructions: Stand upright, legs hip-width apart, while holding onto a stable surface in front of you
bend one knee behind you and lift your foot off the floor
rise onto the toes of your standing foot, hold for 2 seconds
lower back down and repeat

title: hip hike
instructions: Begin standing upright on a step
lower one leg off the step and let your foot hover above the floor
engaging your core move your hip up and down
stay strong on your standing leg without locking your knee

title: stepping forward on heel back on toe (Heel- Toe Walk (optional name))
instructions: Begin standing upright beside a stable surface, legs hip width apart
lift one leg and step forward, landing on your heel and keeping your toes raised
step backward with the same leg, landing on your toes and keeping your heel raised
repeat

title: Goblet squat
instructions: Stand upright with your feet wide, knees slightly bent and toes facing outward
hold a a weight close to your stomach
squat down toward the floor while pushing your hips back and keeping your back straight
push back to standing and repeat

title: Eccentric heel raise
instructions: Stand with your feet hip-width apart, while holding onto a stable surface in front of you
rise up to the toes of your feet, then lift one foot off the floor
lower the heel of your standing foot slowly to the floor, then lower the other foot back down and repeat

title: 90/90 Shoulder IR
instructions: Wrap a band around a doorknob
stand upright beside the door, feet flat on the floor
grip the end of the band with the hand closest to the door
bend your elbow to 90 degrees, tucking your elbow by your side and holding your hand out in front of you
keeping your elbow tucked by your side, rotate your hand inward toward your stomach, creating resistance in the band
hold for 2 seconds, then slowly release and repeat

title: Row
instructions: Wrap the middle of a band around a doorknob and grab both ends with your hands
stand upright, legs hip width apart
engage your core, then squeeze your shoulderblades together, bringing your elbows straight back
hold for 2 seconds, the return to starting position and repeat

title: mini squat
instructions: Begin standing upright with your legs hip-width apart
press your hips back, bend your knees, and lower your body slightly, hinging at your hips
push your heels into the floor and straighten your legs, returning to standing

title: hip extension elbows on chair
instructions: Begin standing in front of a stable surface
bend your elbows and lower your arms onto the surface, keeping your shoulders relaxed
squeeze your buttocks and lift one leg straight back, keeping your back straight
hold for 2 seconds, then lower and repeat

title: hip extension bent knee/ elbows on chair
instructions: Begin standing in front of a stable surface
bend your elbows and lower your arms onto the surface, keeping your shoulders relaxed
squeeze your buttocks and lift one leg back, bending your knee and raising your foor toward the cieling
hold for 2 seconds, then lower and repeat

title: standing double support
instructions: Begin standing next to a stable surface
engage your core
bring both feet together and hold in this position

title: Walk sideways with band above knee
instructions: Begin standing upright with a band wrapped around your thighs
take a step to the side then bring your standing foot to meet the other leg
continue until time is up

title: half tree pose, knee forward
instructions: Stand upright and engage your core
begin shifting your weight toward one foot and slide the other foot below the standing knee, the lifted knee facing forward

title: Triceps stretch with small towel
instructions: Sit or stand while holding a small towel behind your back between both hands
one hand should be lowered over your shoulders and the other lifted behind your back, each grasping one end of the towel
lift your raised elbow toward the cieling and hold

title: Triceps exercise with band
instructions: Sit or stand and place a band behind your back, one hand lowered over your shoulders and the other lifted behind your back
using your lower hand as an anchor, extend your raised elbow toward the cieling, hold for 2 seconds
lower and repeat

title: hip abduction supine
instructions: Lie on your side, legs outstretched and stacked
rest your head on your lower arm
use your other arm to maintain balance
lift your top leg up, no more than 45 degrees, without shifting your hips or pelvis
hold for 2 seconds then lower down and repeat

title: hip abduction supine w band
instructions: Lie on your side, legs outstretched and stacked
wrap a band around your thighs
rest your head on your lower arm
use your other arm to maintain balance
pull your belly button in to engage your core, this will help to stabilize your spine and pelvis
lift your top leg up, no more than 45 degrees, without shifting your hips or pelvis
hold, for 2 seconds, then lower down and repeat

title: Seated knee flexion stretch
instructions: Sit on a chair with your feet flat on the floor
cross your un-affected leg in front of your affected side push back until you feel a stretch in the front of your knee and hold

title: chair push ups
instructions: Sit on a chair with armrests, back straight and feet flat on the floor
holding on to both arm rests, push yourself up off the seat until your elbows are straight (or as far as you can go)
slowly lower down into the chair and repeat

title: buttock Kicks (prone knee flx)
instructions: Lie flat on your stomach with your legs stretched out
bend one leg back, reaching your heel toward your buttocks
bring your foot back down to the floor
repeat

title: Eccentric hip flexion
instructions: Begin by lying on a bed with one knee bent and foot flat on the bed
wrap a band around the opposite foot that is closer to the ledge
holding on to the band with both hands, raise your leg towards the ceiling keeping your knee straight
then allow the band to slip through your hands as you control descent of the leg with your muscles and lower towards the floor
repeat

title: bridge with ball
instructions: Lie on your back with your knees bent, feet flat on the floor
place a ball between your knees and squeeze
press your heels down to lift your hips up off the floor
hold in the up position for 2 seconds
lower down and repeat

title: supine clamshell222
instructions: Lie on your back with one knee bent, foot flat on the floor, your other leg outstretched
slowly lower your bent knee out to the side, rotating your hip outward
then return to the starting position and repeat

stand up, and walk about 10 feet (3 meters), turn around at the cue, walk back to the chair, and sit back down
stay seated for 3 seconds before taking out your phone and finishing your test

title: Functional Reach Test
instructions: Instruct the patient to stand next to, but not touching, a wall and raise one arm to 90 degrees of shoulder flexion, fingers extended
center the camera on the tip of the longest digit (usually the 3rd) and press the plus button
instruct the patient to “reach as far as you can forward without taking a step”
center the camera at the end point (again on the tip of the longest digit) and press the plus button
click the "submit" button

title: Dual task
instructions: You will walk at your normal speed while counting backwards in increments of 3
we will provide you with the starting number
please count out loud, it is ok of you count slowly
if you make a mistake or forget your place, just keep subtracting 3 from the last number
you should be wearing comfortable shoes during this activity
find a flat surface, either inside or outside, with a space to walk continuously with no distractions
you should try to walk in a straight line, but it is ok to turn around and walk back and forth if needed
before you start, place your phone in your pocket
you can stop when you hear the sound “recording stopped”, or see the a blue screen that says “analyzing”
